"review_level": "None",
"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:11.6.2.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">11.6.2.2</span> 標題：大文錢（kodrantes）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： κοδράντης</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： kodrantēs)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:26\">MAT 5:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:42\">MRK 12:42</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/UBS-0038_kodrantes.jpg\" alt=\"提庇留時期的四分硬幣（quadrans或kondrantes），幣值近似一仙\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">提庇留時期的四分硬幣（quadrans或kondrantes），幣值近似一仙 (© Kwo-Wei Peng by United Bible Societies)</figcaption></figure>大文錢：</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:26\">MAT 5:26</a> ：大多數譯本譯作，「直到你付清最後一便士」（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> ）。另外，也可以不指明錢幣就清楚表達這一點；例如，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 和PV 英文意為，「直到你把所有欠的債都還清。」然而，有些學者認為這裡的意思更有可能是：「直到你付清法官判定的罰款。」比較<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ，該譯本的英文意為，「直到你付清罰款的最後一便士」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"God&#x27;s Word Translation\">GW</abbr> 類似）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:42\">MRK 12:42</a> ：這節經文末尾的希臘文本字面意為「兩個lepta，即一個kodrantes」。許多譯本略微擴展「兩個lepta」，譯為「兩個小銅幣」（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> ），然後指出這兩個小銅幣的價值很小，說它們只值「一便士」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 直譯）、「幾分錢」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 直譯）、「不到一分錢」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"God&#x27;s Word Translation\">GW</abbr> 直譯）、「約一便士」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 直譯），「面值很低」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Spanish Common Language Version (Dios Habla Hoy)\">SPCL</abbr> 直譯）。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Italian Common Language Version\">ITCL</abbr> 省略了第二個短語，因為在原文中，這個短語是為了向馬可的讀者解釋他們不太知道的<em>lepton</em> 一詞的價值。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
